sudo raspi-config
	Expand Filesystem(Not needed in Stretch)
	Change Password
		rfid
	Internationalization Options
		Change Timezone
			Asia/Kolkata
		Change Keyboard Layout
			Dell 101 Key PC
		Wifi Country
			India
	Advanced Options
		SSH
		SPI

Setup LAN/Wifi
	LAN in Jessie
		Static IP for LAN - https://www.modmypi.com/blog/tutorial-how-to-give-your-raspberry-pi-a-static-ip-address
	LAN in Stretch(have to use dhcpcd.conf)
		https://www.raspberrypi.org/forums/viewtopic.php?t=191140 
	Wifi - just use the GUI to connect

